  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suit up and save the day in Project Demigod, a physics-driven superhero sandbox with limitless possibilities - now with social multiplayer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick from a huge range of classic and innovative powers including flight, strength, super speed and more. Head to a range of massive locations from sprawling cities to massive arenas and take on missions, fight waves of enemies and topple enormous bosses. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLE POWER SETS, INFINITE POSSIBILITIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix and match a massive arsenal of classic and original superpowers on the fly. Create explosions with one hand, summon a water tentacle with the other, dash through enemies at super speed, and take out the enemies your way. Experiment to discover wild new combos—then take them for a spin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/71a971fff9f1baeaa614375b5af5d5ae.poster.avif?t=1764706477\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/71a971fff9f1baeaa614375b5af5d5ae.webm?t=1764706477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/71a971fff9f1baeaa614375b5af5d5ae.mp4?t=1764706477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLAYER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Social Multiplayer and Drone Combat is now in game! Fight Drones, Turrets, and the new Attack Helicopters together. Swing, fly, race, or just hang out with other Demigods in seamless multiplayer! (Full enemy combat is coming soon in a future update!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/9c6171e1e8d4a9cf1a7f0e51ec8ccf82.poster.avif?t=1764706477\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/9c6171e1e8d4a9cf1a7f0e51ec8ccf82.webm?t=1764706477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/9c6171e1e8d4a9cf1a7f0e51ec8ccf82.mp4?t=1764706477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MODS: UNLEASH THE COMMUNITY!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suit up as your favorite heroes, battle legendary Villains, and wield iconic weapons with built-in mod support via Mod.io. Download new content with a click, or use the Demi-Mod SDK to build and share your own ideas. The only limit is your imagination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/4b354c1c442a055df03303a3e4627e58.poster.avif?t=1764706477\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/4b354c1c442a055df03303a3e4627e58.webm?t=1764706477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/4b354c1c442a055df03303a3e4627e58.mp4?t=1764706477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AN EVOLVING SUPERPOWER PLAYGROUND</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Project Demigod is constantly expanding. New powers, maps, missions, enemies, and features are in development and released regularly—so there’s always a new way to test your might.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/badeddbd6dcd343b6d08ed2532eaef15.poster.avif?t=1764706477\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/badeddbd6dcd343b6d08ed2532eaef15.webm?t=1764706477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/badeddbd6dcd343b6d08ed2532eaef15.mp4?t=1764706477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suit up and save the day in Project Demigod, a physics-driven superhero sandbox with limitless possibilities - now with social multiplayer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick from a huge range of classic and innovative powers including flight, strength, super speed and more. Head to a range of massive locations from sprawling cities to massive arenas and take on missions, fight waves of enemies and topple enormous bosses. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLE POWER SETS, INFINITE POSSIBILITIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix and match a massive arsenal of classic and original superpowers on the fly. Create explosions with one hand, summon a water tentacle with the other, dash through enemies at super speed, and take out the enemies your way. Experiment to discover wild new combos—then take them for a spin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/71a971fff9f1baeaa614375b5af5d5ae.poster.avif?t=1764706477\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/71a971fff9f1baeaa614375b5af5d5ae.webm?t=1764706477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/71a971fff9f1baeaa614375b5af5d5ae.mp4?t=1764706477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLAYER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Social Multiplayer and Drone Combat is now in game! Fight Drones, Turrets, and the new Attack Helicopters together. Swing, fly, race, or just hang out with other Demigods in seamless multiplayer! (Full enemy combat is coming soon in a future update!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/9c6171e1e8d4a9cf1a7f0e51ec8ccf82.poster.avif?t=1764706477\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/9c6171e1e8d4a9cf1a7f0e51ec8ccf82.webm?t=1764706477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/9c6171e1e8d4a9cf1a7f0e51ec8ccf82.mp4?t=1764706477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MODS: UNLEASH THE COMMUNITY!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suit up as your favorite heroes, battle legendary Villains, and wield iconic weapons with built-in mod support via Mod.io. Download new content with a click, or use the Demi-Mod SDK to build and share your own ideas. The only limit is your imagination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/4b354c1c442a055df03303a3e4627e58.poster.avif?t=1764706477\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/4b354c1c442a055df03303a3e4627e58.webm?t=1764706477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/4b354c1c442a055df03303a3e4627e58.mp4?t=1764706477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AN EVOLVING SUPERPOWER PLAYGROUND</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Project Demigod is constantly expanding. New powers, maps, missions, enemies, and features are in development and released regularly—so there’s always a new way to test your might.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/badeddbd6dcd343b6d08ed2532eaef15.poster.avif?t=1764706477\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/badeddbd6dcd343b6d08ed2532eaef15.webm?t=1764706477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646580/extras/badeddbd6dcd343b6d08ed2532eaef15.mp4?t=1764706477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
